INSERT INTO customers (
	company,
	last_name,
	first_name,
	email_address,
	job_title,
	business_phone,
	home_phone,
	mobile_phone,
	fax_number,
	address,
	city
)
VALUES (
	'{{insert_form.formData.company}}',
	'{{insert_form.formData.last_name}}',
	'{{insert_form.formData.first_name}}',
	'{{insert_form.formData.email_address}}',
	'{{insert_form.formData.job_title}}',
	'{{insert_form.formData.business_phone}}',
	'{{insert_form.formData.home_phone}}',
	'{{insert_form.formData.mobile_phone}}',
	'{{insert_form.formData.fax_number}}',
	'{{insert_form.formData.address}}',
	'{{insert_form.formData.city}}'
);
